---
import Image from "astro/components/Image.astro";
import CanadaImg from "@assets/img/country-img/Frontenac-Castle-Old-Quebec-City-Canada.webp";
---

<section>
  <div class="united-stats-area pt-120">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-6">
          <div class="united-states">
            <style>
              .text-center {
                text-align: center !important;
              }

              .tab-pane {
                display: none;
              }
              .tab-pane.active {
                display: block;
              }
              .nav-tabs {
                flex-direction: column;
              }
              .nav-tabs .nav-link {
                border: 1px solid #dee2e6;
                border-radius: 0.25rem;
                margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
              }
              .nav-tabs .nav-link.active {
                background-color: #007bff;
                color: white;
              }
            </style>
            <h2 class="united-states__title mb-15">Study in Canada</h2>
            <!-- <Image src={CanadaImg} alt="" height="500"/> -->
            <p class="mb-30">
              Choose Canada for your studies and move forward in your academic journey. A world-class education, a variety of cultural experiences, and breathtaking natural landscapes are all
              available to students who study in Canada. Also, you will find famous, world-class universities and a good culture. This will help you get different opportunities and experiences, along
              with a quality education. Canada has a wide range of settings for academic pursuits, from bustling cities like Toronto and Vancouver to peaceful mountain towns.
                        </p>
            <p class="mb-25">
              Students can learn about multicultural communities, engage in research on global issues, and take part in year-round outdoor activities. Canada draws students from all over the world who
              are looking for high-quality education and exciting opportunities. Studying in Canada promises to be an enriching and unforgettable experience that will profoundly shape studentsâ€™
              futures.
                        </p>
          </div>
          <div class="cta-wrap" style="display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: start;">
            <span class="col-6 theme-btn" style="margin-right: 20px;">Read More</span>
            <span class="col-6 theme-btn2">Get Assistance</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-6">
          <Image src={CanadaImg} alt="Canada Image" />
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
